STATE of North Carolina
v.
Dwight PARKER, Sr. No. 306P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 5, 2005. Dwight Parker, Sr., Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Clark Everett, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 21st day of June 2004 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Pitt County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th day of February 2005."
